下面的代码片段用于反转单链表，请进行（ ）修改，使其能正确实现相应功能。

```cpp
ListNode* reverseLinkedList(ListNode* head) {
    ListNode* prev = nullptr;
    ListNode* current = head;
    while (current != nullptr) {
        ListNode* next = current->next;
        current->next = next;
        prev = current;
        current = next;
    }
    return prev;
}
```
